IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
Port 993
User yaslam0x1@gmail.com
PassCmd +"$HOME/stuff/get-email-pass.sh isync-yaslam0x1@gmail.com"

IMAPStore outlook-remote
Host imap-mail.outlook.com
SSLType IMAPS
Port 993
User YUZi54780@outlook.com
PassCmd +"$HOME/stuff/get-email-pass.sh YUZi54780@outlook.com"

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

MaildirStore outlook-local
Path ~/Mail/outlook/
Inbox ~/Mail/outlook/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel sync-gmail-default
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both
MaxMessages 400
SyncState *

Channel sync-gmail-drafts
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Near :gmail-local:drafts
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel sync-gmail-sent
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :gmail-local:sent
Create Near
SyncState *

Channel sync-gmail-bin
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Bin"
Near :gmail-local:bin
Create Near
SyncState *

Group gmail
Channel sync-gmail-default
Channel sync-gmail-sent
Channel sync-gmail-bin
Channel sync-gmail-drafts

Channel outlook
Far :outlook-remote:
Near :outlook-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns * !"Junk" !"Mailspring" !"Archive" !"Notes" !"Outbox" !"Sync Issues"
SyncState *
MaxMessages 400
